<!DOCTYPE html><html><head><meta charset='UTF-8'><meta name='viewport' content='width=device-width,initial-scale=1'>
<title>Baby Memory Book</title>
<style>
body{margin:0;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;background:linear-gradient(#fff8f6,#eefcf5);color:#444}
.hero{height:100vh;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center;align-items:center;text-align:center}
h1{font-size:3rem;margin:0}
.btn{padding:12px 24px;border-radius:30px;background:#ffb6b9;color:#fff;text-decoration:none}
section{max-width:900px;margin:auto;padding:60px 20px}
.cards{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(220px,1fr));gap:18px}
.card{background:#fff;border-radius:18px;padding:18px;box-shadow:0 8px 18px rgba(0,0,0,.08)}
.gallery{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(180px,1fr));gap:12px}
.ph{height:180px;background:#ddd;border-radius:14px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center}
footer{text-align:center;padding:30px}
</style></head>
<body>
<div class='hero'><h1>Henza Zehak</h1><p>Every tiny moment becomes a forever memory 💛</p><a class='btn' href='#mem'>Open Memory Book</a></div>
<section id='mem'><h2>Milestones</h2><div class='cards'>
<div class='card'><h3>👶 First Smile</h3><p>A beautiful beginning.</p></div>
<div class='card'><h3>👣 First Steps</h3><p>Little feet, big journey.</p></div>
<div class='card'><h3>🎂 First Birthday</h3><p>One year of happiness.</p></div>
</div></section>
<section><h2>Gallery</h2><div class='gallery'>
<div class='ph'>Photo 1</div><div class='ph'>Photo 2</div><div class='ph'>Photo 3</div><div class='ph'>Photo 4</div>
</div></section>
<section><h2>Letter</h2><div class='card'>Dear Henza, may your life be filled with love, laughter and beautiful memories.</div></section>
<footer>Made with ❤️</footer>
<script>
document.querySelectorAll('.card').forEach(c=>{c.onmouseover=()=>c.style.transform='translateY(-5px)';c.onmouseout=()=>c.style.transform='translateY(0)'});
</script></body></html
